{"tid":2119591,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸醫護片段","createTime":"2020-07-22T07:45:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T09:07:02.000Z","uid":67640,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ef2ba903f237cf94a570a7850fb04a5928387ced","tid":2119591,"uid":67640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:45:32.000Z","msg":"777想引入大陸醫護，知道大家未清楚香港同大陸醫護分別。<br />\n而家幫幫手share 下佢地既片 <br />\n學習定啦 費時入到黎 唔熟行情 冇人理你就唔好<br />\n<br />\n片 片 片<br />\n可以既話分享埋比身邊人睇下"},{"pid":"b54a2ba6e2089c2a9fd247c24c277fd4a8588707","tid":2119591,"uid":359022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:47:18.000Z","msg":"舊聞binC<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n節錄2011年蘋果新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20110510/QQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20110510%2FQQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=2c506978\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20110510%2FQQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4%2F&h=5bcbe452\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20110510/QQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即使海外回來的註冊護士考試及格率也不足四成，<span class=\"red\">內地者更低，更有人連考三次仍不及格</span><br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n立法會議員余若薇表示最近收到投訴，一名在內地有18年工作經驗的資深護士，來港後發現很難搵工，故到護管局查詢報考註冊試的情況，結果發現單是填寫申請表格也極複雜，「<span class=\"red\">連填份表都咁難</span>，佢哋連考試嘅機會都冇」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"teal\">申請表都唔識填 點寫排版</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n節錄2014 西方日報 不貼link<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">三次不合格 失重考資格</span><br />\n<br />\n在內地任職護士逾十年的陳女士來港後，以海外護士資歷申請報考香港護士管理局的登記護士執業試。該考試要求若考生三次不能通過執業試，包括筆試及實習試，除非得到特別許可，否則會失去重考資格。<br />\n<br />\n陳聲稱通過筆試後，卻在實習試的考核中遭不公平待遇。她指，實習試要求考生在一小時內完成兩至三項操作，如<span class=\"red\">洗傷口、包紮及攙扶病人</span>等，惟考室規則各有不同，考核前並無通知考生。「A考室畀你一個鐘內做晒所有操作；B考室就要求每個操作做三十分鐘，時間冇得累積」。她指，考室的<span class=\"red\">洗手盆過低</span>，亦令考生難以符合無菌洗手的要求。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"teal\">三十分鐘一個都完成唔到 好意思投訴考試不公</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"teal\">簡單扶抱都唔掂</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">黎到香港只會幫倒忙 <br />\n多謝曬中國資深護士</span></span>"},{"pid":"ef1db9bf570e7c61c1f4ae19099719ee9af655cf","tid":2119591,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b54a2ba6e2089c2a9fd247c24c277fd4a8588707","tid":2119591,"uid":359022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T07:47:18.000Z","msg":"舊聞binC<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n節錄2011年蘋果新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20110510/QQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20110510%2FQQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4%2F&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB80oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=2c506978\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20110510%2FQQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4%2F&h=5bcbe452\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20110510/QQAQLV2AXEYIM55734TZ24ZHY4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即使海外回來的註冊護士考試及格率也不足四成，<span class=\"red\">內地者更低，更有人連考三次仍不及格</span><br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n立法會議員余若薇表示最近收到投訴，一名在內地有18年工作經驗的資深護士，來港後發現很難搵工，故到護管局查詢報考註冊試的情況，結果發現單是填寫申請表格也極複雜，「<span class=\"red\">連填份表都咁難</span>，佢哋連考試嘅機會都冇」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig